<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to SPRINKLR, <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up for Sprinklr.  Never fear!  Your grass will always be green, and your water bills will be under control with our individualized recommendations.
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for filling out the information about your yard.  Your watering day is <%= @user.yard.day %>.  We will send you a <%= @user.contact_method %> the night before with your personalized recommendation.  Follow the link for even more detailed data. </p>
    <p>
      To update your information or view your recommendations, just login to to the site: <%= @url %>.
      You will log-in through your Google account: <%= @user.login_email %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>